"Tu solicitud de membresía/cuenta sigue activa. Para eliminar estos datos, "
"usa el enlace «dejar la red» de cualquier correo electrónico de Agnosis, o "
"pide ayuda a un administrador."

#: includes/Core/Privacy.php:495
msgid ""
"Your biography, statement, and portfolio link were erased. Your email "
"address was kept on file — your account is currently banned, and it's the "
"only way this site can continue to enforce that."
msgstr ""
"Se eliminaron tu biografía, declaración y enlace al portfolio. Se conservó "
"tu dirección de correo electrónico; tu cuenta está actualmente bloqueada, y "
"es la única forma en que este sitio puede seguir haciendo cumplir eso."

#: includes/Core/Privacy.php:569 includes/Core/Privacy.php:641
msgid "[message removed]"
msgstr "[mensaje eliminado]"

#: includes/Core/Privacy.php:580
msgid ""
"Vouch messages you wrote were redacted. Governance votes you cast were kept "
"as-is — a vote is a community record, not personal data, and removing it "
"would silently change a settled decision."
msgstr ""
"Los mensajes de apoyo que escribiste fueron redactados. Los votos de "
"gobernanza que emitiste se conservaron tal cual: un voto es un registro de "
"la comunidad, no datos personales, y eliminarlo cambiaría en silencio una "
"decisión ya tomada."

#: includes/Core/Privacy.php:623
msgid ""
"Past newsletter delivery records were anonymized; per-issue delivery counts "
"were kept for statistics."
msgstr ""
"Los registros de entrega de boletines anteriores se anonimizaron; se "
"conservaron los recuentos de entrega por número para fines estadísticos."

#: includes/Core/Privacy.php:690
msgid ""
"Agnosis is a federated art-publishing plugin. The following is a starting "
"point for describing what it collects — review and adapt it to your site's "
"actual configuration before publishing."
msgstr ""
"Agnosis es un complemento federado de publicación artística. Lo siguiente es "
"un punto de partida para describir qué recopila; revísalo y adáptalo a la "
"configuración real de tu sitio antes de publicarlo."

#: includes/Core/Privacy.php:691
msgid "What personal data we collect and why"
msgstr "Qué datos personales recopilamos y por qué"

#: includes/Core/Privacy.php:692
msgid ""
"When you apply to join, we store your email address, display name, "
"biography, statement, and portfolio link to run the community vouching "
"process. When you email us artwork, a biography, or an event, the content of "
"that email (including your address) is stored while it is processed and "
"reviewed. When you subscribe to our newsletter or message an artist through "
"their contact form, we store your email address (and, for contact messages, "
"your IP address) to deliver that message or send you future issues."
msgstr ""
"Cuando solicitas unirte, almacenamos tu dirección de correo electrónico, "
"nombre para mostrar, biografía, declaración y enlace al portfolio para "
"llevar a cabo el proceso de apoyo de la comunidad. Cuando nos envías por "
"correo electrónico una obra, una biografía o un evento, el contenido de ese "
"correo (incluida tu dirección) se almacena mientras se procesa y revisa. "
"Cuando te suscribes a nuestro boletín o envías un mensaje a un artista a "
"través de su formulario de contacto, almacenamos tu dirección de correo "
"electrónico (y, en el caso de los mensajes de contacto, tu dirección IP) "
"para entregar ese mensaje o enviarte futuros números."

#: includes/Core/Privacy.php:693
msgid "Who we share it with"
msgstr "Con quién lo compartimos"

#: includes/Core/Privacy.php:694
msgid ""
"Submitted artwork descriptions and images may be sent to a third-party AI "
"provider (OpenAI or Anthropic, depending on this site's configuration) to "
"help write publication text and enhance images. If this site instead uses "
"WordPress's own built-in AI Client (configured under Settings → Connectors), "
"submitted content is sent to whichever AI service that connector points to "
"instead. Approved posts are also broadcast publicly over ActivityPub (the "
"Fediverse) as part of this plugin's core federation feature."
msgstr ""
"Submitted artwork descriptions and images may be sent to a third-party AI "
"provider (OpenAI or Anthropic, depending on this site's configuration) to "
"help write publication text and enhance images. If this site instead uses "
"WordPress's own built-in AI Client (configured under Settings → Connectors), "
"submitted content is sent to whichever AI service that connector points to "
"instead. Approved posts are also broadcast publicly over ActivityPub (the "
"Fediverse) as part of this plugin's core federation feature."

#: includes/Core/Privacy.php:695
msgid "How long we retain your data"
msgstr "Durante cuánto tiempo conservamos tus datos"

#: includes/Core/Privacy.php:696
msgid ""
"Retention varies by data type; see this site's administrator for specifics. "
"You can request a copy of, or the erasure of, the personal data described "
"above at any time using this site's standard WordPress data request tools."
msgstr ""
"La conservación varía según el tipo de datos; consulta al administrador de "
"este sitio para obtener detalles. Puedes solicitar en cualquier momento una "
"copia o la supresión de los datos personales descritos arriba mediante las "
"herramientas estándar de WordPress para solicitudes de datos de este sitio."

#: includes/Core/Privacy.php:724
msgid ""
"Submitted text and images may be processed by a third-party AI provider. "
"Approved posts are published publicly and shared across the Fediverse — this "
"cannot be fully undone later."
msgstr ""
"El texto y las imágenes enviados pueden ser procesados por un proveedor de "
"IA externo. Las publicaciones aprobadas se publican públicamente y se "
"comparten en todo el Fediverso; esto no puede deshacerse por completo "
"después."

#: includes/Core/Privacy.php:725
msgid ""
"Your message may be reviewed by an automated content filter before being "
"sent to the artist."
msgstr ""
"Tu mensaje puede ser revisado por un filtro de contenido automatizado antes "
"de enviarse al artista."

